  "text": "14-16 The 9-and 12-repeat alleles have been shown to enhance transcription of SERT compared with STin2. 10. 17,18 In people with long-term medical conditions, the 5-HTTLPR s/s and STin2 9/12 genotypes were more frequent in patients with comorbid depression. [CITATION_1] The study goal is to determine whether the odds of PSD are similarly heightened in carriers of alleles previously associated with mental illness: the 5-HTTLPR s allele and the STin2.9 and STin2.12 alleles.",
